					"value": "<p>If the victim succeeds at a saving throw against this curse while in sunlight, the curse ends. While you have this curse, you bypass the resistance of the wraith that cursed you;</p><p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[will|dc:37]</p><hr /><p><strong>Stage 1</strong> the victim is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.TkIyaNPgTZFBCCuh]{Dazzled} in any light (1 hour)</p><p><strong>Stage 2</strong> the victim gains lifesense 30 feet but is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.XgEqL1kFApUbl5Z2]{Blinded} in any light (1 hour)</p><p><strong>Stage 3</strong> as stage 2, but the creature also has @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.bestiary-ability-glossary-srd.Item.TTCw5NusiSSkJU1x]{Void Healing} (1 hour)</p><p><strong>Stage 4</strong> the victim becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.fBnFDH2MTzgFijKf]{Unconscious} and can't awaken (1 day)</p><p><strong>Stage 5</strong> the creature dies and becomes a wraith, its body crumbling to ash</p>",
